title: ENABLE_MOON_CYCLE_OVERRIDE
content:
0x2C328AF17210F009// EnableMoonCycleOverride
void ENABLE_MOON_CYCLE_OVERRIDE(float phase);Parameters:phase: A value indicating the moon cycle.Enable a custom moon cycle, allowing control of which lunar phase the moon is in.Valid values are from 0.0 to 1.0, with 0.5 representing a full moon.ValueLunar Phase0.1Waxing Crescent0.2First Quarter0.3Waxing Gibbous0.5Full Moon0.7Waning Gibbous0.8Third Quarter0.9Waning CrescentThe moon phase can be disabled with DISABLE_MOON_CYCLE_OVERRIDEOld name:  _SET_EXTRA_TIMECYCLE_MODIFIER_STRENGTHExamples:LuaEnableMoonCycleOverride(0.5)
